quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  17,97,"Oon mo Alla feewni ko oon woni peewu…óo, …ďe o majjini …ďe a he…ďantaa…ďe walloo…ďe ko woori mo. Min moo…ďay …ďe √Īande darnga e dow je'ece ma…ď…ďe …óe ko …ďe wum…ďe e muum…óu…ďe= fahdube …ďe e faa…óu…ďe, ja'a∆īndee ma…ď…ďe nden ko jahannama tuma kala nge rocci min …ďeydana …ďe hu…ď…ďunge."
  17,98,"∆äuum ko njo…ďdi ma…ď…ďe, sabu kam…ďe …ďe njeddii aayeeje amen …óe, …ďe mbi'i i: "E hay si min ngonii ∆īi'e e mbu…óu e hara minen ko min immintintee…ďe tagoore?!" hesre."
  17,99,"Enee, …ďee nji'aani, won'de Alla O Tak…óo kammuuli …ói e leydi ndi ko kattan…óo nde o tagata yeru ma…ď…ďe, o wa…óani …ďe lajal [caate] sikke alaa e maggal. Too√Īoo…ďe …ďe calii si wonaa jeddugol."
  17,100,"Maaku: "Sinndo onon ho…óon marnoo ngaluuji yurmeende e Joomi am on, on tuma, on njogitotono kulol nafkugol, ne…ó…óaŇčke on wonii nguddo"."
  17,101,"GooŇč…óii min n ngkkiino Muusaa aayeeje jeenay …ďanngu…óe, lanndii …ďi…ď…ďe Israa'iila …ďen tuma nde o arnoo …ďe Fir'awna wi'ani mo: "min dey mi…óo sikkumaa ko an yo Muusaa ko a mbil…óaa…óo"."
  17,102,"Maaku: "GooŇč…óii ha…óa anndi jippinaani …óee si wonaa Jey…óo kammuuji …ói e leydi ndi aayeeje [yi'etee…ói]. Min dey mi…óo sikkumaa ko an yo Fir'awna ko a kalkii…óo"."
  17,103,"O faalaa nde o dillinta …ďe ka lesdi min n njoooli mo e …ďe won'du …ďe e makko …ďe denndaangal."
  17,104,"Min Daalani …ďaawo makko …ďi…ď…ďe Israa'iila …ďe: "Ho…óee ka leydi, si fodoore sakkitiinde nden arii, min ngaddana on ko on muu…ďii…ďe=fiiliibe"."